title: Revenue of the Minnesota Vikings ( NFL ) 2001 to 2018
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Revenue in million U.S. dollars, containing a total of 18 data points.
Overall Revenue in million U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015 and 2016.
The highest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 427.0 was reached at Year 2018
The lowest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 123.0 was reported at Year 2001
